            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Subsection 2.4 -->
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 flex items-center">
            <span class="h-8 w-8 rounded-lg bg-purple-100 text-purple-700 flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold mr-3">2.4</span>
            Fees and Payment
          </h3>
          <div class="bg-amber-50 rounded-2xl p-6 border border-amber-200">
            <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
              All membership, Vetting, and Certification fees (including the CDTCO Program) are payable upon invoice. All fees are <strong class="text-slate-900">non-refundable</strong>, except as otherwise stipulated in a separate written membership agreement or required by Canadian consumer protection law.
